<title>USA: Mesa Inc names Jon Brumley chairman, CEO.</title>
<headline>Mesa Inc names Jon Brumley chairman, CEO.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1996-08-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Mesa Inc said Thursday its board elected Jon Brumley chairman and chief executive, succeeding Boone Pickens in the posts, effective immediately.  </p>
<p>Brumley was most recently chairman and CEO of Cross Timbers Oil Co, which he co-founded.</p>
<p>Pickens, once a renowned corporate raider, said in June that he would retire once a successor was hired.</p>
<p>He will remain on Mesa's board.</p>
<p>--New York Newsdesk 212-859-1610.</p>
</text>
